  • Method Details

    • uiReadyMedicalContactStatus

      public static MedicalContactStatusBuilder uiReadyMedicalContactStatus()
      Creates a new, ui ready, MedicalContactStatusBuilder with the following fields set
      • Claim - if a claime is specified via onExposure or by using exposureBuilder.withMedicalAction then use the specified exposure. Otherwise a new ui ready medical details exposure is created.
      • CommunicationDate - set to a unique date before today
      • InfoSource - a randomly selected info source
        Returns:
        a new ui ready builder
